<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='ja'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, maximum-scale=1'>
    <title>kosenconf tokyo</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:400,700" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='./style.css'>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <header id='header'>
        <h1>
          <span class='h1-one'>KOSEN Conference</span>
          <span class='h1-two'>in Tokyo 2018</span>
        </h1>
        <time>2018/07/15 sun. 10:00~</time>
      </header>
      <section id='theme'>
        <div class='theme-block'>
          <div class='theme-block-header'>
            <h2>開催テーマ</h2>
          </div>
          <div class='theme-block-content'>
            <div>
              <p class='theme-ja'>多様化する技術との巡りあい</p>
              <p class='theme-en'>Say hello to dynamic technologies</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id='links'>
        <nav>
          <a class='btn btn1' href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfmLTFutgrYm84Ky1KPNU9-MI09rr9i99SDGHA4dFurP1UBEQ/viewform">一般発表に応募する</a>
          <a class='btn btn2' href="https://connpass.com/event/87606/">参加登録する</a>
        </nav>
      </section>
      <% if false %>
      <section id='schedule'>
        <h2>
          <span class='h2-one'>Schedule</span>
          <span class='h2-two'>発表プログラム</span>
        </h2>
        <div class='timetable'>
          <%- data.timetable.each do |prog| -%>
            <div class='tt-row'>
              <div class='tt-time'><%= prog.time %></div>
              <div class='tt-avatar'><img alt='avatar' src='<%= prog.avatar %>'></div>
              <div class='tt-content'>
                <p class='tt-title'><%= prog.title %></p>
                <p class='tt-speaker'><%= prog.speaker %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          <%- end -%>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id='sponsors'>
        <h2>
          <span class='h2-one'>Sponsors</span>
          <span class='h2-two'>出資企業様のご紹介</span>
        </h2>
        <div class='sponsors'>
          <%- data.sponsors.each do |sponsor| -%>
            <div class='sponsor'>
              <div class='sponsor-img'><img alt='logo' src='<%= sponsor.logo %>'></div>
              <h3><%= sponsor.name %>様</h3>
              <p><%= sponsor.description %></p>
            </div>
          <%- end -%>
        </div>
      </section>
      <% end %>

      <section id='access'>
        <h2>
          <span class='h2-one'>Access</span>
          <span class='h2-two'>アクセス</span>
        </h2>
        <div class='access-map'>
          <iframe class='access-map' frameborder="0" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=AIzaSyAsCnOl492oX_U4oCvmDH9Pe360HHq1twM&q=%E4%BD%8F%E5%8F%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A3%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%A8%E3%82%B0%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%83%89%E3%82%BF%E3%83%AF%E3%83%BC" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
        <h3></h3>DMMグループセミナールーム</h3>
        <p>東京都港区六本木三丁目2番1号 住友不動産六本木グランドタワー24階</p>
        <p>南北線六本木一丁目駅直結</p>
        <p>日比谷線・大江戸線「六本木駅」から徒歩5分</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
